                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="~/images/banner1.svg" alt="ASP.NET" class="d-block w-100">
            <div class="carousel-caption ">
                <h5> Learn how to build ASP.NET apps that can run anywhere.</h5>
                <p>
                    <a class="btn btn-primary text-light" href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=525028&clcid=0x409" rel="noreferrer">
                        Learn More..
